ActFreshwater Fish Marketing Act
PrecisApproval of the appointment by the Minister of Fisheries and Oceans of THOMAS COLOSIMO of Hay River, Northwest Territories, to be a director of the Board of Directors of the Freshwater Fish Marketing Corporation, to hold office during pleasure for a term of three years, in the place of Bert Buckley, whose term has expired.
